            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "INDIVIDUAL AND GROUP VARIATION IN ECHOLOCATION CALLS OF BIG BROWN BATS, EPTESICUS FUSCUS (CHIROPTERA: VESPERTILIONIDAE)",
            "creators": [
